OL,3,CWhy is an independent regulator being
OL,4,Cestablished in English football?
OL,6,FCoined the Football Governance Bill,
OL,7,Fthe legislation will underpin the
OL,8,Fcreation of an independent regulator
OL,9,Ffor English football, which will
OL,10,Flicense clubs in the top five tiers of
OL,11,FEnglish football.
OL,13,FAmong the regulator's key
OL,14,Fresponsibilities, will be ensuring
OL,15,Fclubs are financially sustainable,
OL,16,Fmaking the sport more financially
OL,17,Fresilient between leagues and
OL,18,Fsafeguarding English football's
OL,19,Fheritage.
OL,21,FWhy is it being introduced?
