OL,11,FWhat powers will the regulator have?
OL,13,FThe government has long warned
OL,14,Ffootball authorities that a regulator
OL,15,Fwould have 'backstop powers' to settle
OL,16,Fthe ongoing row over financial
OL,17,Fdistribution between the Premier
OL,18,FLeague and the EFL (English Football
OL,19,FLeague).
