OL,3,CWhy is an independent regulator being
OL,4,Cestablished in English football?
OL,6,F"These powers mean that if the leagues
OL,7,Ffail to agree on a new deal on
OL,8,Ffinancial distributions, then the
OL,9,Fbackstop can be triggered to ensure a
OL,10,Fsettlement is reached," a government
OL,11,Fannouncement on the Bill said.
OL,13,FPrecise details over the point at
OL,14,Fwhich the powers would be triggered -
OL,15,Fand what those powers would look like
OL,16,F- have not yet been confirmed, but the
OL,17,Fgovernment said in a consultation
OL,18,Fresponse last September that one
OL,19,Foption it was considering was binding
OL,20,Ffinal offer arbitration.
