OL,3,CWhy is an independent regulator being
OL,4,Cestablished in English football?
OL,6,FUnder that system, the two leagues
OL,7,Fwould each submit their proposal, the
OL,8,Fregulator would assess them against
OL,9,Fpredetermined criteria, and then would
OL,10,Fchoose and impose one as the binding
OL,11,Farrangement.
OL,13,FAs of yet, Premier League clubs have
OL,14,Fnot come to a majority consensus on
OL,15,Fthe size of a a financial package to
OL,16,Foffer the EFL, with the Premier League
OL,17,Fsaying its clubs are focused on first
OL,18,Fagreeing new financial rules for the
OL,19,Ftop flight.
