OL,3,CWhy is an independent regulator being
OL,4,Cestablished in English football?
OL,6,FPrimarily, the regulator will, once
OL,7,Festablished, be concerned with
OL,8,Fsafeguarding the financial
OL,9,Fsustainability of clubs in England
OL,10,Fthrough a licensing system - covering
OL,11,Fclubs from the National League up to
OL,12,Fthe Premier League.
OL,14,FNon-compliance of this could result in
OL,15,Fthe regulator inflicting a fine of up
OL,16,Fto 10% of turnover on clubs, the
OL,17,Fgovernment said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/14
