OL,3,CWhy is an independent regulator being
OL,4,Cestablished in English football?
OL,6,FAdditionally, it will have the power
OL,7,Fto block clubs from competing in
OL,8,Funapproved competitions, a nod to the
OL,9,Foutrage among fans caused by England's
OL,10,F'Big Six' - Manchester City,
OL,11,FManchester United, Liverpool, Chelsea,
OL,12,FArsenal and Tottenham Hotspur -
OL,13,Fseeking to form a European Super
OL,14,FLeague.
OL,16,FThe government intends the regulator's
OL,17,Flicensing regime to be "proportionate"
OL,18,Fand said it will involve a system of
OL,19,Fprovisional and full licences, to give
OL,20,Fclubs time to transition.
