OL,3,CWhy is an independent regulator being
OL,4,Cestablished in English football?
OL,6,F"We agree it is vital that football
OL,7,Fclubs are sustainable, remain at the
OL,8,Fheart of their communities and that
OL,9,Ffans are fundamental to the game."
OL,11,FEFL Chairman Rick Parry said: "The EFL
OL,12,Fwelcomes today's arrival of the
OL,13,FFootball Governance Bill to Parliament
OL,14,Fin what we hope will be an important
OL,15,Fmilestone to help us secure the long-
OL,16,Fterm financial sustainability of
OL,17,FEngland's football pyramid."
