OL,3,CWhy is an independent regulator being
OL,4,Cestablished in English football?
OL,6,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak said: "For
OL,7,Ftoo long some clubs have been abused
OL,8,Fby unscrupulous owners who get away
OL,9,Fwith financial mismanagement, which at
OL,10,Fworst can lead to complete collapse -
OL,11,Fas we saw in the upsetting cases of
OL,12,FBury and Macclesfield Town.
OL,14,F"This Bill is a historic moment for
OL,15,Ffootball fans - it will make sure
OL,16,Ftheir voices are front and centre,
OL,17,Fprevent a breakaway league, protect
OL,18,Fthe financial sustainability of clubs,
OL,19,Fand protect the heritage of our clubs
OL,20,Fbig and small."
